---
name: seo-content-brief-generator
description: Create an SEO-ready content brief with intent mapping, structure, and internal linking plan.
version: 1.0.0
authors:
  - sravanth
tags:
  - seo
  - content
  - brief
  - marketing
model:
  api: chat
  configuration:
    type: openai
    api_key: ${env:OPENAI_API_KEY}
    model: ${env:OPENAI_MODEL_CHAT:gpt-4o-mini}
  parameters:
    temperature: 0.3
    top_p: 0.95
    max_tokens: 1400
inputs:
  topic:
    type: string
    description: Core topic to target.
  audience:
    type: string
    description: Target persona.
  funnel_stage:
    type: string
    enum:
      - TOFU
      - MOFU
      - BOFU
    default: TOFU
  primary_keyword:
    type: string
    description: Main keyword for the article.
  secondary_keywords:
    type: string
    description: Comma-separated secondary keywords.
  competitors_summary:
    type: string
    description: Optional summary of top competitor pages.
    default: ""
outputs:
  type: object
  schema:
    type: object
    properties:
      title_options:
        type: array
        items:
          type: string
      meta_description:
        type: string
      search_intent:
        type: string
      outline:
        type: array
        items:
          type: object
          properties:
            heading:
              type: string
            level:
              type: string
            key_points:
              type: array
              items:
                type: string
          required:
            - heading
            - level
      internal_link_targets:
        type: array
        items:
          type: string
      cta:
        type: string
      differentiation_ideas:
        type: array
        items:
          type: string
    required:
      - title_options
      - meta_description
      - search_intent
      - outline
      - internal_link_targets
      - cta
sample:
  topic: fastapi middleware best practices
  audience: backend engineers at startups
  funnel_stage: MOFU
  primary_keyword: fastapi middleware
  secondary_keywords: request id, logging middleware, cors setup
  competitors_summary: Most articles cover only CORS and miss observability patterns.
---

system:
You are an SEO strategist and technical editor.
Create practical content briefs with specific structure and clear differentiation.
Output valid JSON only matching the declared schema.

user:
Build a content brief using:
- topic: {{topic}}
- audience: {{audience}}
- funnel_stage: {{funnel_stage}}
- primary_keyword: {{primary_keyword}}
- secondary_keywords: {{secondary_keywords}}
- competitors_summary: {{competitors_summary}}

Requirements:
- Include primary keyword naturally in at least one title option.
- Keep meta_description at 155 characters or fewer.
- Keep outline actionable, not generic.
